    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a masterclass in atmospheric induction. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. This unit features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox paired with a torque-sensing M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been meticulously executed: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system overhauled with uprated seals, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates to mitigate chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping characteristics, and the hydraulic steering rack remains tight and communicative. The exterior is finished in its original paint with no swirl marks or rock chips, while the interior features immaculate Nappa leather and an uncracked dash. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning enthusiast.",
